{"tid":433031,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯縱橫球壇三十餘載，殺盡獌蝗，敗盡英雄，天下更無抗手。","createTime":"2017-10-12T04:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T08:20:56.000Z","uid":54373,"like":9,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"03c0473a875f19418b620c0ce9f97bf1ccd30bc6","tid":433031,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:57:14.000Z","msg":"縱橫球壇三十餘載，殺盡獌蝗，敗盡英雄，天下更無抗手，無可奈何，惟隱居加泰，以蘇狗為友。嗚呼，生平求一敵手而不可得，誠寂寥難堪也。\t&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n凌厲剛猛，無堅不摧，弱冠前以在紐維爾群雄爭鋒。<br />\n<br />\n球王盤紐，三十歲前所用，誤傷賤朗不祥，悔恨無已，乃棄之深谷。<br />\n<br />\n重劍無鋒，大巧不工，四十歲前持之橫行天下。<br />\n<br />\n四十歲後，不滯於物，草木竹石均可為足球。自此精修，漸進於無波勝有波之境。"},{"pid":"befd28bebfd86c1231485e35091eef8199cdb78e","tid":433031,"uid":74751,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T05:15:03.000Z","msg":"好老鑑"},{"pid":"e1c51e30af0d2515c3942659509f2df5e8fa9acb","tid":433031,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T11:23:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61bff59b5f9f60be189a1e2ee724f8610e9f4680","tid":433031,"uid":35176,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T11:29:14.000Z","msg":"死撚開啦9527"},{"pid":"bd26413817bca52a8037f7656a4e7c97a19b0388","tid":433031,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:54:21.000Z","msg":"佢對史高斯果下直角假星真係完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b40314ce1ac43b2cc4506eef2f93caad0acc804","tid":433031,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T01:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ea09621545590905601a070d39d64a27b9e9e8","tid":433031,"uid":131176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T01:03:57.000Z","msg":"0歲開始踢波"},{"pid":"9ef326d6f60b006194829e88a73f91e21f15e1ce","tid":433031,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T01:07:49.000Z","msg":"siuma<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d816c131c6015758cbf3fc460ec6ec91a7ac7ef","tid":433031,"uid":28758,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T02:18:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好老鑑</blockquote><br />\n咁你咪唔好睇囉"},{"pid":"63c5bb13a36fc3fa709906629db9350399433892","tid":433031,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T02:24:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢對史高斯果下直角假星真係完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n保定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f594893c122b41c1a2e35bf67a89b0436b9c6f9b","tid":433031,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T06:08:51.000Z","msg":"問過車仔未"},{"pid":"1ebcdd3af23ebf94f9ce1b2bcff1b887afd500e8","tid":433031,"uid":152823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T07:29:10.000Z","msg":"獨波求敗"},{"pid":"4b31904d2aeedf542f509cf283b25d175e8738f8","tid":433031,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T07:31:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問過車仔未</blockquote><br />\n車仔=玄慈方丈"},{"pid":"f3a31c1310e69188602ad40c7525bce581bdeddd","tid":433031,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T07:31:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好老鑑</blockquote><br />\n樓主抄我半年前篇文，將c朗個名轉做美斯"},{"pid":"fbe94e0969f6a77ecb1665f15809d3687a6ae48a","tid":433031,"uid":15842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T07:50:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好老鑑</blockquote><br />\n樓主抄我半年前篇文，將c朗個名轉做美斯</blockquote><br />\n你抄金容"},{"pid":"b47c2c1400d963e6892c1ede520d4ba428350a4b","tid":433031,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T08:20:56.000Z","msg":"一天美斯和夏薩特來訪。聊著聊著，突然外頭跑來一隻狗。這隻狗還有個名字，叫&ldquo;蘇亞雷&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n就在這個時候，美斯心中突生一計，要取笑C朗拿度，便道：&ldquo;咦，你們瞧那是狼是狗？&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\nC朗拿度知道美斯在捉弄他，當下也不動聲色的說：&ldquo;要分辨狗或狼有兩種方法。一種是看它的尾巴，尾巴下垂的是狼，尾豎是狗。&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n一旁的夏薩特大笑道：&ldquo;哈哈，我還道那是狼是狗呢，原來尾豎是狗，哈哈，哈。&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n此時C朗拿度不慌不忙的接著又說道：&ldquo;另一種分辨的方法就是看它拉屎。狼是回巢排糞，狗則隨地下撒。&rdquo;這下子連夏薩特也噤聲無言了。"}]}